An open-source and free wallet implementation for the Android runtime, based on [[bitcoinj|BitCoinJ]]. It requires either Android 2.3 (or newer) or Black Berry OS 10 (or newer). It was first released on March 7, 2011 (1.1). As of January 2014, it is being used by 400.000 people.

